The [[University of St. Michael's College|University of St. Michael<U+2019>s College]] held a two-day event,  "Celebrating Sheila," on October 24 and 25, 2009, to mark the 100th anniversary of Watson<U+2019>s birth and the 50th anniversary of the publication of ''The Double Hook''.<ref name=fonds/>

