*''Five Stories''. Toronto: Coach House P, 1984.
*''A Father's Kingdom: The Complete Short Fiction''. Toronto: McClelland & Stewart, New Canadian Library, 2004.<ref>"[http://www.amazon.ca/Fathers-Kingdom-Complete-Short-Fiction/dp/0771034881 A Father's Kingdom: The Complete Short Fiction] [Mass Market Paperback]", Amazon.ca, Web, Apr. 22, 2011.</ref> ISBN 0-7710-3488-1 ISBN 978-0771034886

===Essays===
*"A Question of Portraiture." ''The Tamarack Review'' (Autumn 1963).
*"The Great War: Wyndham Lewis and the Underground Press." ''arts/canada'' (Winter 1965).
